data.description: Beautiful two-story masterpiece boasts a captivating limestone and brick exterior, meticulously landscaped to enchant every visitor. Custom-crafted by Gehan Homes in 2016, this gem sits nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering a sanctuary of comfort and style. With 4,102 square feet thoughtfully designed to cater to every need, including wider exterior and interior doorways perfect for accessibility, this home is a haven for all. As you step inside, be greeted by the grandeur of 8-foot interior doors on the first floor, leading to not one but two primary bedrooms and bathrooms—one conveniently located downstairs, ideal for easy living, and another upstairs for added privacy and convenience. With a total of 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, there's ample space for family and guests to unwind in luxury. Need a home office? Discover the elegance of a separate office space with charming French doors, while a media room and bonus room offer endless possibilities for relaxation and entertainment. Entertain in style in the soaring-ceiling living room, complete with a cozy fireplace and seamless flow into the gourmet kitchen adorned with granite counters, a center island, gas cooktop, wall oven, and microwave—perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Host unforgettable dinners in the formal dining room, or savor quiet moments in the living room. Retreat to the sizeable secondary bedrooms, each boasting a walk-in closet for added convenience. A spacious laundry room with a second refrigerator adds practicality to luxury living. Outside, discover your own private oasis—a generous .24-acre lot with an expansive backyard and convenient storage shed, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. Plus, enjoy the perks of community living with access to a pool and playscape. With its prime location close to downtown and major employers, this is more than a home—it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the Open House Sat. 2/10 12-4 & Sun. 2/11 11-1.
